Package ReadWriteFile

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TextFileReader
    An interface that will contain the necessary methods to read text files
    TextFileWriter
    An interface that will contain the necessary methods to write to the data .txt files
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CourseIndexReader
    This will read the courseData.txt file and return an arraylist of CourseIndex items
    CourseIndexWriter
    This class implements the TextFileWriter interface in order to write the data from the CourseIndex database manager into the data .txt file
    StaffReader
    This will read the staffdata.txt file and return an arraylist of StaffAcc objects
    StudentReader
    This will read the studentdata.txt file and return an arraylist of StudentAcc objects
    StudentWriter
    This class implements the TextFileWriter interface in order to write the data from the Student database manager into the data .txt file
